Open the py file in VS Code or application or website that can run Python code
Press "Run" button

For the Minimum Heap program
Type in the data in integer one by one
After inputting one data, press enter and type the second one
After you type all the data you need to type, Input "-1" for ending the input section
The program will give out the smallest and the second smallest result

For the Heap Sort program
Typr in all the data you want to type in in a space-seperated form, like[2 4 5 6 1 3]
Do not type in one by one or with a "," between each data
The program will give out an array of the data you type in in ascending order
